TextElement.Str: Would you like for me to remove your Marvel offline library files? This will remove all the files as well as remove their database entries.

Action.Str: Changing Folder Name to Match Title
Moving Finished Products and Removing Temporary Files
if [ -d "%localPath" ]; then echo 1; else echo 0; fi
I was unable to find the Marvel offline folder.
if [ ! -d /sdcard/comics ]; then mkdir /sdcard/comics fi if [ ! -d /sdcard/comics/sources ]; then mkdir /sdcard/comics/sources fi if [ ! -d /sdcard/comics/cbz ]; then mkdir /sdcard/comics/cbz fi

if [ ! -f /system/xbin/zip ]; then mount -o remount,rw /system mv /sdcard/comics/zip /system/xbin chown root:root /system/xbin/zip chmod 0755 /system/xbin/zip mount -o remount,ro /system echo 0 else rm -f /sdcard/comics/zip echo 0 fi

if [ -f /system/xbin/sqlite3 ] || [ -f /data/xbin/sqlite3 ] || [ -f /system/bin/sqlite3 ]; then echo 0
else echo 1 fi
Clearing Library, hold on a sec
mount -o remount,rw /system mv /sdcard/comics/sqlite3 /system/xbin chown root:root /system/xbin/sqlite3 chmod -R 0755 /system/xbin/sqlite3 mount -o remount,ro /system echo 0
